---
layout: component.njk
title: Carousel
description: Image and content slider with neumorphic prev/next controls, dot indicators, autoplay, and multiple visible items.
componentId: carousel
hasControls: false
toc:
  - Default
  - With Dots
  - Loop
  - Loop Rewind
  - Multiple Items
  - Multiple with Cards
  - With Gap
  - Autoplay
  - Vertical
---

{% set g = [
